SYMBOL RELEASE FLOW

Symbol release flow is using GIT VERSIONING
Below are some standardizations and rules which we need to follow for maintaining robust , secure and scalable codebase.
This rules will enable us to maintain and release symbol effectively and effeciently with minimum efforts.

---

- WE ARE USING GIT HOOKS FOR EFFECTIVELY MINIMIZING ERROS IN DEVELOPMENT ENVIRONMENT
- Also for maintaining consistency in each commit of project we are using commit-msg hook. We have specified some formate and standards for commits.

MAJOR.FEATURE.PATCH
v1.0.0
major | feature | patch

commit message will be
type-of-commit:status:msg
type-of-commit : [majr , conf , docs , perf, fix , rtn , feat , patch , bug]
status : [done , indev , blocked]
